a.xlink:title: main loads in configurations and initiates program according to .json specifications.
Parallel::Communicator::init initializes the communicater and sets up the lattice geometry.
Header containing functions needed for running unit tests, integration tests and validation testing.
runPerformanceTests will run performance tests on program. Exits once complete.
System::latticeSetup sets up the lattice geometry and allocates memory.
System::run based on passed parameters, does one of three things:
Parallel::Index::setNTot sets the total lattice dimensionality.
Parallel::Communicator::setN sets the lattice dimensions in the Parallel::Communicator class.
Parallel::Index::setN sets the sub lattice dimensionality.
